descriptionHtml:
[center][b][size=4]DISCLAIMER[/size][/b]
This is a character preset for a fairly young character (Though, definitely 18) and I recommend quite a few high-pitched voice mods, so this may not be for everyone. [/center][size=2]
[center]So, I've been modding Skyrim for 6-7 years and I've spent a lot of time trying to make my characters as cute as possible. Here's what I have so far, folks. She's a [b]female Breton[/b]. This preset may or may not be compatible with other races.[/center]
[b][size=4]
Requirements: [/size][/b][/size]
Calient's Beautiful Bodies Edition (CBBE)
Fair Skin Complexion
Enhanced Character Edit
XP32 Maximum Skeleton (version 3.93)

[b][size=4]Present in preset, but probably not required, but still highly recommended:[/size][/b]
Eyes of Aber or Eyes of Beauty (I THINK Eyes of Beauty is the one I've mainly been using.)
SG Female Eyebrows
SG Hair Pack

[size=3]I've tested a Skyrim with all of the above mentioned mods (and also 'alternate start' for quicker testing purposes) and there's no issues other than there being a big issue with the torso if you install XP32MS before ECE. So, under "Requirements", [b]download them in the order that I listed[/b], and you should have no issues. Also be sure to [b]install XP32MS version [u]3.93[/u][/b], I don't remember what it was, but when I updated I had issues with the preset and I didn't want to fix it. Sorry for the inconvenience.[/size]

[b][size=4]Other recommended mods for your character: [/size][/b]
Ahri Voice Replacer or Young female voice replacer (I use my own custom voice mod that is a combination of these 2 (mostly AVR), I may link that instead later, once I get permission from the uploaders)
Lore Friendly Female Anime Voice Shout
Mofu animations (there's a link on the nexus, but it's not updated completely so much that it doesnt even half of of all the animations. I highly recommend searching google for the latest version)
Pretty Jump Animations
Realistic Animation Project - Movement
Feminine Hands CBBE UNP
Customizable Camera

[size=4][b]Clothing/Armor/Accessory mods used in screenshots: [/b][/size]
Project Sekirei
Zlushka Stockings for CBBE
Osare Gothic Lolita - UNP
Wa Ribbon
Chevalresse II HDT-SMP
Girls Heavy Armors - CBBE
Light Bow
Dovahbling Jewelry Replacer
Ultimate Assortment

[b][size=3]Permissions:
[/size][/b]You can use this preset for whatever. You don't really have to mention me for credit, but it would be appreciated.

[b][size=3]Installation: [/size][/b]
Download Winrar to unzip the file, then move it "_1_commonTriRaces.slot" into your CME_save folder that comes with ECE. It's typically at C:\Users\[Name]\Documents\My Games\Skyrim\CME_save
author: izanagi33
